                $"\"Beta channel on\". Likely the user-block case-'b' arm at " +
                $"server/src/PlayerConnection.cpp:5519 changed shape, the body-block " +
                $"AdminLevel>=BETA guard at PlayerConnection.cpp:5521 inverted, the BETA " +
