    ///   <item>
    ///     %s format-substitution NEW MIDDLE 4-byte width regression
    ///     at <c>PlayerClass.cpp:3422</c>. Catalogue had 7 distinct
    ///     widths (1/3/5/6/7/11/13/14) -- Wave 146 adds 4-byte,
