    /// (AdminLevel=100 >= DEV=80) but signature/setradius/setradius/
    /// shutdown/sendp/strings/stats/shieldbuff all mismatch against
    /// pch="script". case-'s' breaks at 7458. NET RESULT: ONE emit.
