    ///     /warp NO-OUTER-GUARD INSIDE-BODY-GM; Wave 160 at case-'t'
    ///     /trade pure NO-GUARD CONSECUTIVE-IF. FIVE distinct NO-
    ///     GUARD pins across THREE distinct case-letters (t/u/w) AND
