    /// <summary>
    /// Wave 163 sibling-arm-pinning hardening (+0 ratchet, 0x0033
    /// CLIENT_CHAT -&gt; 0x001D MESSAGE_STRING via slash short-circuit):
    /// pins the byte-exact 33-byte wire-shape of the single 0x001D
