    /// at 7704 (COLOR=5 default). NET RESULT: exactly 1 emit "Illegal
    /// slash command: /zzzzzz" (30B, COLOR=5). Wire: `[u16 LE 31][u8 5]
    /// [30B ASCII "Illegal slash command: /zzzzzz"][NUL]` = 34 bytes.
