    /// First admin-tier case-'e' MatchOptWithParam ERROR-fork pin. FIFTH
    /// admin-tier NO-INLINE-GUARD pin (joins //halloween 4927,
    /// //restartcomms 5055, //countsp 4831, //displayplayerfaction 4865).
    /// FIRST admin-tier pin where the case body uses two PLAIN `if`s
    /// (rather than else-if chain) -- catches regression where a
    /// maintainer collapses the structure into else-if and accidentally
    /// changes single-emit semantics if both options ever happened to
    /// match (they cannot today, but the regression coverage pins the
    /// invariant against future arm additions).
    /// </para>
    ///
    /// <para>Budget: 90s.</para>
    /// </summary>
